"Yes, and I confess that the contents startled me beyond measure. Have you good authority for what
you say?"

"The best possible."

Lord St. Simon sank into a chair and passed his hand over his forehead.

"What will the Duke say," he murmured, "when he hears that one of the family has been subjected to
such humiliation?"

"It is the purest accident. I cannot allow that there is any humiliation."